descriptionHTML:
Diamonds lover? Impress your friends with your new watchface.
Move your wrist to experience gyroscope enhanced glittering effect.
Choose between silver or golden finish.

Features:
- silver and gold face (settings),
- ambient mode.

Designed for Android Wear.
Supported smartwatches: LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Motorola Moto 360, Sony SmartWatch 3, Asus ZenWatch, Samsung Gear Live.
comments: Shuts off too soon and defaults to a boring watch face
